You're staring at me. Why?

652
00:38:03,699 --> 00:38:04,741
I'm looking.

653
00:38:05,742 --> 00:38:06,743
Nothing more.

654
00:38:08,829 --> 00:38:11,165
And I'm thinking
how fortunate my cousin is

655
00:38:11,248 --> 00:38:13,459
