656
00:38:16,003 --> 00:38:18,755
So why do you allow him to... shame you?

657
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:22,676
Cnut, you know nothing,

658
00:38:23,427 --> 00:38:24,678
so you will say nothing.

659
