704
00:41:39,748 --> 00:41:40,957
My wife.

705
00:41:41,249 --> 00:41:42,292
Another one?

706
00:41:43,710 --> 00:41:44,836
How many is that?

707
00:41:46,296 --> 00:41:51,635
